---
title: Beef Koftas & Mint Sauce with Roasted Veggies & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Although koftas come from the meatball family, they shine on their own as flavour powerhouses. Bring out those delicious tastes with a mint sauce on top alongside a side of roast cauliflower and veggies.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

